      "correctAnswer": "A",
      "explanation": "E[X] = 1\u00d70.3 + 2\u00d70.5 + 3\u00d70.2 = 0.3 + 1.0 + 0.6 = 1.9.",
      "difficulty": "easy"
    },
    {
      "id": "mcq-13",
      "question": "For X ~ Bin(8, 0.5), what is Var(X)?",
